==================
contenttypes.basic
==================

This addon provides the common content-types. fields, widgets and behaviors.

Features
--------

- Permissions
- Indexers
- Behaviors
- Fields
- Content-types
    - Announcement
    - Banner
    - Icon
    - Slide
- Widgets
    - Colour
    - Icon
    - Map


Translations
------------

This product has been translated into

- Catalan
- Spanish
- English


Installation
------------

Install contenttypes.basic by adding it to your buildout::

    [buildout]

    ...

    eggs =
        contenttypes.basic


and then running ``bin/buildout``



Classifiers
-----------

Framework

- Plone 5.2

Programming Language

- Python 3.6
- Python 3.7


